---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="技术博客 | JY Portfolio">
  <section class="article-page">
    <header class="article-header">
      <p class="eyebrow">Blog</p>
      <h1>技术博客</h1>
      <p>记录 AI Agent、RAG、LLM 应用工程化和求职项目复盘。</p>
    </header>

    <div class="post-list">
      <a class="post-card" href={`${base}blog/jobpilot-agent-engineering-notes/`}>
        <span>AI Agent Engineering</span>
        <h2>如何把 LLM Demo 做成可写进简历的 Agent 项目</h2>
        <p>从单次 Prompt 调用升级到可运行、可评测、可展示的工程系统。</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
